Lycorhinus angustidens
Haughton, 1924 - 
Thulborn (1970
, Figs 1-5); 
Gow (1975
, 336, Figs 1, 2, pl. 1); 
Hopson (1975
, Figs 1, 2, 3a, b, e); 
Hopson (1980
, Figs 2, 3); 
